      "acf_fc_layout": "block_text_fh",
      "title": "Welcome to Huronia Maxillofacial Radiology",
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "text": "Huronia Maxillofacial Radiology comprises two oral and maxillofacial imaging clinics operated by Dr. Grace Petrikowski, providing diagnostic imaging and radiographic consultation services for dental patients."
        },
        {
          "text": "We offer conventional radiography, cone beam computed tomography (CBCT) for a variety of clinical applications, clinical photography, and radiographic interpretation and consultation services. We also provide written reports for CBCT and plain film studies done in other offices and support easy file upload for external studies."
        }
      ],
